We create our reality with the repeated thought we think in our mind. 
So...if what you are thinking lately becomes your reality would you be happy with it?

Mind is like monkey, always repeating, the way we think the same old, what we fear, how we respond....same....over and over again! 

UNTILL........,we train it to think Differently
UNTILL........,we train it to think Creatively 
UNTILL........,we train it to think Positively 
UNTILL........,we train it to think Lovingly 
UNTILL........,we train it to think Abundantly

If you reallllyyy love yourself, you would choose positive thoughts, because, it's good for your life❤️️
Love YourSelf, Heal Your Life❤️️
Let us train our mind to think better and love ourselves and others more❤️️

“Perfection is a disease of a nation. We overlay our faces with tons of make-up. We get botoxs and even starve ourselves to become that perfect size. We try to fix something but you can’t fix what you can’t see. It’s the soul that needs the surgery. It’s time that we take a stand. How can you expect someone else to love you if you don’t love yourself? You have to be happy with yourself. It doesn’t matter what you look like on the outside, it’s what’s on the inside that counts. Today, I want to put up a makeup-free photo. I know I have wrinkles on my skin but today I want you to see beyond that. I want to embrace the real me and I want you to embrace who you are, the way you are, and love yourself just the way you are.” – 

- #JuliaRoberts

What each one of us is looking for is true acknowledgement of Self and others. Let's begin with Self-Acceptance and see how healing and transforming it is!

Join us for the Kolkata batch of 'Love YourSelf, Heal Your Life' workshop on 17-18 Dec!
